item.title: CVE-2020-16238|2024-08-04T13:37:53.954Z -- b.%20braun%20melsungen%20ag -- spacecom
item.description: A vulnerability in the configuration import mechanism of the B. Braun Melsungen AG SpaceCom Version L81/U61 and earlier, and the Data module compactplus Versions A10 and A11 allows attackers with command line access to the underlying Linux system to escalate privileges to the root user.
